						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Achuyutadēva-Mahārāya Year: Śaka 1453, <hi rend="italic">Vikruti</hi>, śu. <hi rend="italic">di Tiruvōṇam</hi> Wednesday = 20th April 1530, but the <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> was <hi rend="italic">bahuḷa.</hi></hi></p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Contains only the names of the territorial divisions Mēlkuṉṟa-nāḍu in Palkuṉṟa-kōṭṭam in Jayaṅgoṇḍachōḻa-maṇḍalam. Other details are lost.</p>						

